<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如来笑着对悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么能这么厉害？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有位圣人教了我很多法术。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我练习了很多年。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我现在可以和玉帝平起平坐了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“玉帝轮回转世多次，一直练习。”如来说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么会认为你可以同玉帝平起平坐？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>快回你的花果山去， 好好做你的美猴王吧!”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不！”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不走，我要统领这天庭。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如来思考了一会儿：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孙悟空，你有什么本事？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以变化成其他动物。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以腾云驾雾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想做什么就能做什么！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那么我们来打个赌吧！”如来说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你赢了，你就可以统领天庭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玉帝会和我一起去西天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你输了，你会受到重罚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要怎么做？”悟空问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很简单。”如来说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他伸出了一只手：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你只需从我的手掌里翻出去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那很简单！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我可以越过整个海洋！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如来也笑了：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那么，我们就来看看你的本事吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳上了如来的手掌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你真愚笨！”他对如来说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会跳得比你想象的要远的多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我回来的时候，就可以统领这天庭了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳到云上，飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他飞了好一阵之后，看到了五根巨大的柱子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在柱子前停下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这一定就是天边了。”他对自己说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在就回去告诉如来，让那玉帝让位。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这天庭是我的了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空刚要回去，突然想起来了点儿什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这儿一个人都没有。”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要怎么证明我来过这里呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他摸了摸下巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我就在这柱子上写句话吧！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如来可以自己来确认。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184146</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空拔下两根毫毛，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184147</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>变出了一支笔和一瓶墨水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在其中一根柱子上写下：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>齐天大圣到此一游。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了！” 悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我就回去告诉如来我跳了多远。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孙悟空又一个跟头翻了回去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了好长时间，他回到了如来的手掌里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我回来了！”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让那玉帝走吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如来皱起了眉头：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么说你回来了？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你从来没离开过我的手掌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空不明白。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我离开了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我到了天边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里有五根巨大的柱子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我还在其中一根柱子上写字了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你可以跟我去看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们哪儿都不用去。” 如来说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你回头看看吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空回头一看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在如来中指靠近底部的地方写着：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>齐天大圣到此一游。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跺脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你耍我！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你一定是用了什么法术！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不是什么法术。”如来说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你从未离开过我的手掌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我离开了！我离开了！”悟空高叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一路跳出了......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你已经输了，孙悟空！”如来说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在你要受到惩罚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如来紧紧握着孙悟空将他放在了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的手掌变成了一座山，压在了孙悟空的身上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”悟空叫了一声，用尽所有力量挣扎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>压在他身上的那座山被抬起了一点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如来从他的衣袖中拿出了一张符咒，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贴在了山顶上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那山又被压了回去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>339350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如来转身对着玉帝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>86</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>339351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>347285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，孙悟空无法再把这座山抬起来了。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>87</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>347286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他会被困在这山下，直到他的惩罚结束。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>